allthrusmartphone.xyz A smartphone lifestyle focused blog authored by Shafat M.
Slowly and steadily we are moving towards a world where our smartphones will dominate everything &ndash; from our life to our education to our business. Through this blog, the author is going to educate and inspire Gen X, Y and Z on how to use this little workhorse for learning, earning, and productivity so that they can better prepare themselves for the future.
Because the author believes, &ldquo;FUTURE is AllThuSmartphone&rdquo;&hellip;
and&hellip; &ldquo;It&rsquo;s in YOUR Hand&rdquo;
So, let&rsquo;s make it happen&hellip;
Disclaimer: While the name of the blog &ldquo;All Thru Smartphone&rdquo; might suggest everything talked here is done through a smartphone, the reality is a little different. Although the author spends most of his time to run his side hustle through smartphone but still, some automation and foundational work requires the use of a laptop as well. If anyone asks how much of the work done through a smartphone, and with a laptop&hellip; it would be fair to say 80/20&hellip;
